fields.description:
A timeless little black dress with added drama. Cut from soft Ponte fabric and featuring voluminous organza sleeves, this dress is perfect for any evening occasion. Pockets at the side seams add a thoughtful and practical detail to this elegant piece.

Viscose blend
Slim fit

Side-seam pockets

fields.name: Personality Karlism T-shirt
fields.description:
A pure cotton T-shirt with personality. This essential graphic T-shirt features the quote, “Personality begins where comparison ends”, from the legendary Karl Lagerfeld. From workday to weekend styling, pair this T-shirt with tailored trousers or your favourite KARL jeans.

Pure cotton
Regular fit
Short sleeves
Crew neck
KARL quotation artwork at the front
Elongated KARL logo at the back of the neck

fields.description:
These high-gloss black leggings will instantly update your wardrobe. The skinny pair is fashioned with Punto stretch-jersey panels at the inner leg for comfort and a sculpted fit. Team yours with sneakers or chunky ankle boots.

Patent coated fabric
Punto jersey inner leg
Concealed side zip
Grosgrain elastic inner waistband
KARL logo rivet at the hip
